---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Privacy"
  description="Privacy notice for Na Hua Kukui."
  canonicalPath="/privacy"
>
  <section class="bg-bg-dark pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-40 md:pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold text-gold mb-6">Privacy</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-bg-light py-24 md:py-32">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 prose-custom">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">What we collect</h2>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        This website does not use cookies. If you contact us via the contact form, we receive your name, email address, and message. This information is used solely to respond to your inquiry and is not shared with third parties.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Analytics</h2>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We may use privacy-friendly analytics (such as Plausible) to understand how visitors use the site. These tools do not use cookies, do not collect personal data, and comply with GDPR, CCPA, and PECR.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Third-party services</h2>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed mb-6">
        If you book a discovery call, you will be directed to Calendly, which has its own privacy policy. We recommend reviewing their terms before booking.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-serif text-xl font-semibold text-accent mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-text/80 leading-relaxed">
        If you have questions about this privacy notice, please email
        <a href="mailto:hello@nahuakukui.com" class="text-gold hover:underline">hello@nahuakukui.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
